channel.title: Shipwreck Silver Set
channel.desc: Secure one of only 93 Sets of 3: 1850 to 1852 Seated Liberty Dimes from the famed SS Central America shipwreck for your collection. Recovered from the purser's safe aboard the SSCA, these coins are graded AU50 and come with a pinch of Gold Rush Dust.
